OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry throughout the day. There
OL,6,Fwill be some low cloud around, this
OL,7,Fmay become persistent across Shetland.
OL,8,FOtherwise some sunny spells, best of
OL,9,Fthe sunshine across western Orkney.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry.
OL,12,FThen the rest of the night will be
OL,13,Fmainly dry and often cloudy, a few
OL,14,Fshowers possible across Orkney later.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FA mainly cloudy day with
OL,17,Foccasional showers, some misty low
OL,18,Fcloud across Shetland. Becoming breezy
OL,19,Facross Orkney.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
