OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,6,Fstart Saturday before outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain spread east in the afternoon and
OL,8,Fevening. Showery rain on Sunday before
OL,9,Fit turns drier on Monday.
